commit.message:
fix: verify upload job ID mismatch + flatten poll response

- POST /ocr/process: return flat { jobId, id, status } instead of nested { data: { id } }
  so frontend can read data.jobId directly (was falling back to temp_ prefix ID)
- GET /ocr/jobs/:id: return flat { id, status, result } instead of { data: job }
  so frontend poll reads data.status correctly

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
